Skill: ftoggle                    GL: Varies       Cost: None
This skill allows you to toggle on|off your various defensive techniques.
The skills you can toggle are: counter, feint, guts, and shieldblock (you
can also use block).
You can also ftoggle the endurance bar on, off, or bar.

The defensive skills use endurance, so you can toggle which you
want running to help you conserve your endurance.

Syntax is: ftoggle <skill> <on|off>
Syntax is: ftoggle endurancebar <on|off|bar>
Syntax is: ftoggle techbar <on|off>

See also: fhelp counter, fhelp feint, fhelp guts, fhelp shieldblock
